\begin{tabular}{|c|c|c|c|l|}\hline
setting & start & object & location & likely locations\\\hline
1 & 1 & remote & 1 & living room, hotel room, home office\\\hline
2 & 3 & remote & 1 & living room, hotel room, home office\\\hline
3 & 1 & mouse & 2 & home office\\\hline
